/>\n<br />\n住得偏僻，食得的式"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"歐洲酒店 , $435 一晚 , 平到笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53835eef298ae51d48107d1bec59c49ccd02b642","tid":1802180,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"924b78002a060dff7cc4d6fde293ccee140b67be","tid":1802180,"uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"西班牙叫「Help！Help！」，侍應笑容滿面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"可能唔識聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://translate.google.com/#view=home&amp;op=translate&amp;sl=en&amp;tl=es&amp;text=Help\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.google.com%2F%23view%3Dhome%26op%3Dtranslate%26sl%3Den%26tl%3Des%26text%3DHelp&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=e4c59b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://translate.google.com/#view=home&amp;op=translate&amp;sl=en&amp;tl=es&amp;text=Help</a>"},{"pid":"c7479c052aeead3da6891c51396d7230878abdf4","tid":1802180,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fb940cd9b44f1d53faebc83d88128a069fb714d","tid":1802180,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e8012964883d5d73fd3871da863289291af525a","tid":1802180,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"間酒店:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/TRYP+Valencia+Almussafes/@39.3068904,-0.4162538,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x0:0x4d55631850c2379!5m2!4m1!1i2!8m2!3d39.306562!4d-0.412792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2FTRYP%2BValencia%2BAlmussafes%2F%4039.3068904%2C-0.4162538%2C17z%2Fdata%3D%214m8%213m7%211s0x0%3A0x4d55631850c2379%215m2%214m1%211i2%218m2%213d39.306562%214d-0.412792&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=f1fecd1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/place/TRYP+Valencia+Almussafes/@39.3068904,-0.4162538,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x0:0x4d55631850c2379!5m2!4m1!1i2!8m2!3d39.306562!4d-0.412792</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n住得偏僻，食得的式"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"歐洲酒店 , $435 一晚 , 平到笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:32:35.000Z","msg":"但附近真係乜鳩都無，過多5-10分鐘車程先係小鎮"},{"pid":"39e157ad6a3308e21ea528603c2861dfee90b764","tid":1802180,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於是周末，<span style=\"color: red;\">大使館</span>關閉，要等周一才可去求助</blockquote><br />\n咩護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a49311aa2826666ab811327a81b08854ca5d69d","tid":1802180,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:38:30.000Z","msg":"支持加泰獨立"},{"pid":"06855b10568ff674268b5830f805ee587f5b8032","tid":1802180,"uid":174432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:43:28.000Z","msg":"下面啲五毛即刻打哂飛機話中国大使館xxxx<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11a8462ffef50638db5390dcca69b0625e2b18c","tid":1802180,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"美麗華可以又拍廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db45136db156873bb1c0c63eb89b2bd5254628d1","tid":1802180,"uid":18692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>中國遊客旅遊巴在華倫西亞被砸窗搶劫 39本護照被盜損失或達數十萬元</strong><br />\n<br />\n2019年5月26日晚上，一個來自中國、由39人組成的旅行團在華倫西亞科學城家樂福附近就餐。飯後發現大巴車遭遇砸窗搶劫，車門被撬，盜賊搶走了10個行李箱，其中裝有39本護照，其他被竊物品經濟價值高達數十萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n當晚，旅行團致電中國駐巴塞隆拿總領館並請求幫助，工作人員告知護照補辦步驟和注意事項，並提醒遊客主動前往華倫西亞當地警察局報案。次日14時左右，位於馬德里的中國駐西班牙使館接到該旅行團來電，報案人稱所在旅行團遭遇盜竊，請求使館幫助。<br />\n<br />\n據遊客反映，「事發後，我們馬上通報了中國駐西班牙大使館和（巴塞隆納）總領事館，人員指點我們馬上報警。國內旅行社也沒有任何安撫的電話。報警後，西班牙警方即不出警也不取證，其辦理效率讓人心寒。」<br />\n<br />\n據領事館人員了解，該團沒有食宿方面的困難，部分團員的常用藥被盜，人員已建議及時購買非處方藥，或就近就診後，根據醫囑購買處方藥。其後旅行團決定繼續西行，到位於里斯本的中國駐葡萄牙大使館補辦護照。<br />\n<br />\n據記者了解，由於遲遲未等到西班牙警方的妥善處理，報案人27日下午致電大使館並得到幫助後，在社交媒體上發布了一條約340字的求助信息，因措辭較為激烈，引發當地華僑華人關注。<br />\n<br />\n近年來，中國遊客因護照被盜申辦旅行證的數量直線上升，充分反映出西班牙治安堪憂。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但為了旅途愉快順利，遊客請務必妥善保管好自己的護照，隨身攜帶，不宜將護照集中放在一起，更不宜放在無人的大巴上的某個行李箱內。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"20f367ddc8cfe4c208ddd90378750064416d3f62","tid":1802180,"uid":174432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39e157ad6a3308e21ea528603c2861dfee90b764","tid":1802180,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於是周末，<span style=\"color: red;\">大使館</span>關閉，要等周一才可去求助</blockquote><br />\n咩護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"條片下面啲五毛已經打哂飛機話香港人咪又係用支那護照<br />\n啲精就嚟淹撚死我<br />\n有冇人可以幫下手"},{"pid":"1ecf866347f2c86be1fb57bb4fc9b55101e17e85","tid":1802180,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由於是周末，<span style=\"color: red;\">大使館</span>關閉，要等周一才可去求助</blockquote><br />\n咩護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>條片下面啲五毛已經打哂飛機話香港人咪又係用支那護照<br />\n啲精就嚟<span style=\"color: red;\">浸</span>撚死我<br />\n有冇人可以幫下手</blockquote>"},{"pid":"edc2aea2972b74735fdb8993101b7d1044200f1c","tid":1802180,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:19:24.000Z","msg":"戰狼在哪?"},{"pid":"0602d2a166706a00640275f6eae89040d1b22f3b","tid":1802180,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ang